name: Flying Air Canada's DOMESTIC PREMIUM ECONOMY! 787-8 Toronto to Calgary [4K]
description:
Over the past few weeks, Air Canada's been flying a number of domestic widebody flights as travel ramps up again, and for the most part, these flights are relatively full.

Relatively full, that is, in Business Class and Economy - but Air Canada also has a Premium Economy cabin on their widebodies that doesn't seem to get much love on domestic flights.

Today, I check out Air Canada's domestic Premium Economy on their 787-8 Dreamliner, with a hint of nostalgia!
